{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for chip component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the chip component tokens you want.","","        override var dividerBorderWidth: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthmediumt }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider: ChipComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(divider: CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(divider: CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    let dividerComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own border semantic tokens providers","    let dividerComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider(","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.13.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"title":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B35ThemeDividerComponentTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider\/init(borders:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider\/borders"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider\/DividerComponentTokens-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[